---
// CustomerSegmentBlock.astro
//
// "Since 2017, hundreds of remarkable organisations trusted us..."
// — verbatim copy from readonlyrest.com per v5 plan §3.2.
// Used on homepage and /regulated.
---

<section class="customer-segments">
  <p class="segment-lede">
    Since 2017, hundreds of remarkable organisations trusted us.
    Customers that make us <strong>extra proud</strong>:
  </p>
  <ul class="segment-list">
    <li>📈 <strong>2× in the S&amp;P 500 top 5</strong></li>
    <li>🧸 <strong>2× Charities protecting children</strong></li>
    <li>⚛️ <strong>3× Nuclear research institutions</strong></li>
    <li>🇪🇺 <strong>2× European Union institutions</strong></li>
    <li>👮‍♀️ <strong>Various government institutions</strong></li>
  </ul>
  <p class="segment-disclaimer">
    Logos and customer references on this site reflect Beshu Tech's
    customer base for ReadonlyREST. Their presence does not imply any
    endorsement, sponsorship, or affiliation with DeltaGlider.
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .customer-segments {
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .segment-lede {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .segment-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .segment-list li {
    margin: 0.4rem 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .segment-disclaimer {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }
</style>
